<h4>Slack Settings</h4>
<p>The Tracker provides integration with Slack, which allows you to be notified whenever a particular action occurs. Before you can enable notifications, be sure to set the channel you want notifications to go to. By default, the Tracker uses the Clan AOD Slack team.</p>

<p>Some events are potentially more spammy than others, so experiment to see what works best for your division.</p>